    <data key="d0">Genomic Data Curation Pipeline</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=53sUjFv9ByI</data>
    <data key="d2">System processes hundreds to thousands of genomic samples. Uses EKS with Auto Scaling to scale from 0 to 100+ nodes to process sporadically run pipelines cost-effectively, persisting versioned scientific pipelines in ECR.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
